// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1943 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 14805b15-460c-58cf-9f7b-3f91c93c16bb

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
